%br/
.jumbotron
  %h1 KimWiki
  %p Welcome to KimWiki, a place for collaboration.
  %p Join us! Users who choose the standard (free) plan can create and view public wikis. Those who choose the premium plan can also create private wikis and collaborate with others on shared interests.

  %p Not ready to commit? You can still view any public wiki. Hope to see you soon!

  %br/
  - if !current_user
    %div{:align => "center"}
      = link_to "Sign In", new_user_session_path, class: 'btn btn-primary'

.container
  .row
    .col-md-6
      %h3{align: :left}
        %span
          %b.name KimWiki
        Standard Plan
      %p Benefits include:
      %li Create public wikis
      %li View public wikis
    .col-md-6
      %h3{align: :left}
        %span
          %b.name KimWiki
        Premium Plan
      %p Benefits include:
      %li Standard Plan benefits
      %b
        %i plus
      %li Create private wikis
      %li Collaborate on private wikis
